		<title>How to return the position, of the first found occurrence of a specified value in a string</title>
		
	</head>

	<body>
		<p>Note this can be the position of a character or position of a word</p>

		<script type="text/javascript">
			
			var str="Hello World"
			document.write(str.indexOf("d")+"<br/>");
			document.write(str.indexOf("WORLD")+"<br/>");
			document.write(str.indexOf(world"));

		</script>

